      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order, making it a dependable choice for daily driving. While the exterior paint still shows a nice shine, there are some minor rock chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though you will notice some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and a few small scuffs on the interior trim. Overall, this is a well-cared-for car that offers a great balance of performance and value without the premium price of a showroom-perfect model.",
