      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-output S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for a broad powerband. This example has undergone extensive preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS rebuild, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis is sharpened with upgraded bushings and a refined suspension setup, maintaining the telepathic steering feel these cars are known for. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust and the rod bearings have been addressed. A true driver\u2019s spec for those who value performance over concours perfection.",
